Company Overview of Tristate Holdings Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Tristate Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs and manufactures garments in the People's Republic of China, Canada, the United States, and the United Kingdom. It also exports garment products. The company offers sportswear, military uniforms, and men’s and women’s wear under the C.P. Company, EFM, Cissonne, and HASKI brand names. It also engages in the branded product distribution, retail, and trading. In addition, the company offers sales liaison, general administrative and supporting, factory facilities leasing, nominee and secretarial, technical, and design and customer support services. Further, it is involved in trademark holding and licensing, as well as general trad...
Tristate Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs and manufactures garments in the People's Republic of China, Canada, the United States, and the United Kingdom. It also exports garment products. The company offers sportswear, military uniforms, and men’s and women’s wear under the C.P. Company, EFM, Cissonne, and HASKI brand names. It also engages in the branded product distribution, retail, and trading. In addition, the company offers sales liaison, general administrative and supporting, factory facilities leasing, nominee and secretarial, technical, and design and customer support services. Further, it is involved in trademark holding and licensing, as well as general trading and marketing, and product design and development activities. The company was founded in 1937 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong. Tristate Holdings Limited is a subsidiary of Silver Tree Holdings Inc.
Detailed Description


